Usage: changeBumpMaster [-help] -bumpMasterName <bumpMasterName>
                        [-fromBumpMasterName <bumpMasterName>]
                        [-location_type {cell_center cell_lowerleft geometry_center geometry_lowerleft}] {-netName <netName> | -allBumps  | -bump_name <bump_list> | -selected }

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-allBumps                            # specifies that all bumps will use the
                                     # new cell master (bool, optional)
-bumpMasterName <bumpMasterName>     # specifies the name of the cell master
                                     # (string, required)
-bump_name <bump_list>               # change bump master on specified bumps
                                     # (string list, optional)
-fromBumpMasterName <bumpMasterName> # specifies the name of the cell master
                                     # (string, optional)
-location_type {cell_center cell_lowerleft geometry_center geometry_lowerleft}
                                     # It specifies the location type. (enum, optional)
-netName <netName>                   # specifies net name bumps connected to
                                     # which will use the new cell master
                                     # (string, optional)
-selected                            # change selected bump(s) with new cell
                                     # master (bool, optional)